	"info": {
		"_postman_id": "72292cdf-8f07-4a9d-9afb-fe7382dc78ef",
		"name": "Izertis",
		"description": "# Películas API\n\nAPI REST para buscar películas y consultar detalles usando OMDB como fuente de datos.\n\n## Autenticación\n\nEste API usa JWT (JSON Web Tokens). Para acceder a los endpoints:\n\n1. Ejecuta la request \"Login\" con credenciales válidas\n    \n2. Copia el token `access` de la respuesta\n    \n3. Úsalo en las demás requests (ya configurado en Authorization)\n    \n\n## Usuarios disponibles\n\n- **username:** usuario1, **password:** pass123\n    \n- **username:** usuario2, **password:** pass123\n    \n- **username:** admin, **password:** admin123\n    \n\n## Base URL\n\n[http://localhost:8000](http://localhost:8000)\n\n## Endpoints\n\n- POST /api/auth/login/ - Obtener tokens JWT\n    \n- POST /api/auth/refresh/ - Refrescar access token\n    \n- GET /api/movies/search/ - Buscar películas\n    \n- GET /api/movies/{imdb_id}/ - Detalle de película\n    \n\n## Autenticación\n\nGuarda automáticamente access_token y refresh_token con métodos en post-response",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
		"_exporter_id": "39373031"
	},
	"item": [
		{
			"name": "Login",
			"event": [
				{
					"listen": "test",
					"script": {
						"exec": [
							"var jsonData = pm.response.json();\r",
							"pm.collectionVariables.set(\"access_token\", jsonData.access);\r",
							"pm.collectionVariables.set(\"refresh_token\", jsonData.refresh);"
						],
						"type": "text/javascript",
						"packages": {}
					}
				}
			],
			"request": {
				"method": "POST",
				"header": [],
				"body": {
					"mode": "raw",
					"raw": "{\r\n  \"username\": \"usuario1\",\r\n  \"password\": \"pass123\"\r\n}",
					"options": {
						"raw": {
							"language": "json"
						}
					}
				},
				"url": {
					"raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/login/",
					"host": [
						"{{base_url}}"
					],
					"path": [
						"api",
						"auth",
						"login",
						""
					]
				}
			},
			"response": []
		},
		{
			"name": "Refresh token",
			"event": [
				{
					"listen": "test",
					"script": {
						"exec": [
							"var jsonData = pm.response.json();\r",
							"pm.collectionVariables.set(\"access_token\", jsonData.access);"
						],
						"type": "text/javascript",
						"packages": {}
					}
				}
			],
			"request": {
				"method": "POST",
				"header": [],
				"body": {
					"mode": "raw",
					"raw": "{\r\n  \"refresh\": \"{{refresh_token}}\"\r\n}",
					"options": {
						"raw": {
							"language": "json"
						}
					}
				},
				"url": {
					"raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/refresh/",
					"host": [
						"{{base_url}}"
					],
					"path": [
						"api",
						"auth",
						"refresh",
						""
					]
				}
			},
			"response": []
		},
		{
			"name": "Buscar películas",
			"request": {
				"auth": {
					"type": "bearer",
					"bearer": [
						{
							"key": "token",
							"value": "{{access_token}}",
							"type": "string"
						}
					]
				},
				"method": "GET",
				"header": [],
				"url": {
					"raw": "{{base_url}}/api/movies/search/?query=matrix",
					"host": [
						"{{base_url}}"
					],
					"path": [
						"api",
						"movies",
						"search",
						""
					],
					"query": [
						{
							"key": "query",
							"value": "matrix"
						},
						{
							"key": "page",
							"value": "1",
							"description": "opcional",
							"disabled": true
						}
					]
				}
			},
			"response": []
		},
		{
			"name": "Detalle de película",
			"request": {
				"auth": {
					"type": "bearer",
					"bearer": [
						{
							"key": "token",
							"value": "{{access_token}}",
							"type": "string"
						}
					]
				},
				"method": "GET",
				"header": [],
